      • populateDays

        public void populateDays(int month)
        Will, depending on the month, fill in the allocated GridPane with accordingly dates and days. This needs to be called before showing activities as it sets a label for the correct day.

        Also lines up with days in the top: Mandag, tirsdag, onsdag, torsdag, fredag, lørdag and søndag.

        Parameters:
        month - from 0-11.

      • showActivities

        public void showActivities(ActivityList activities)
        Show all the activities from the ActivityList to the OverviewMonth. This will remove any previously shown activities.
        Specified by:
        showActivities in interface ShowableActivity
        Parameters:
        activities - Activities to show.
